{lang-eng}Samaadhana desham paralokamu enno deevenalu
Kalavanduna ihaloka shaanti kshana maatrame
Goppa siksha yandu daagiyunde{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Kristu nundi ninnu doora paracha lokaashalu ninnu
Aakarshinchu siluvanu choodaka poyinacho
Chikku konedavu ee lokamulo{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Prabhu Yesu sahavaasamuna nilichi saataanuku
Stala miyyakumu evi kristunundi vidadeeyuno
Yesu rakhtamandu kadugu konumu{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Paraloka deevenalu ruchichoodanu aashatho
Vellanu siddapadu lokamunaku neevu verainacho
Aatmeeyamuga neevu yedigedavu{/lang-eng}
